---
import WidgetLayout from '../../layouts/WidgetLayout.astro';
---
<WidgetLayout title="ProgressBar">
  <h1>ProgressBar</h1>
  <p>Fill container with flexbox children. Fill paints background with inverted colors over the filled region.</p>

  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <pre><code>&lt;ProgressBar value={0.13} width={60}&gt;
  &lt;Text&gt;Downloading update (436)&lt;/Text&gt;
  &lt;Text&gt;13%  814kB/s  2m30s&lt;/Text&gt;
&lt;/ProgressBar&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>Preview</h2>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░
Downloading update (436)                       13%  814kB/s  2m30s
^^^^ inverted ^^^^                           ^^^^ normal ^^^^</pre>

  <h2>Accessible mode</h2>
  <p><code>Downloading update (436) -- 13%</code></p>

  <h2>Props</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>value</td><td>number</td><td>0 to 1</td></tr>
      <tr><td>width</td><td>number</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>children</td><td>ReactNode?</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>filledStyle</td><td>CellStyle?</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>emptyStyle</td><td>CellStyle?</td><td></td></tr>
      <tr><td>indeterminate</td><td>boolean?</td><td>animated, no value needed</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Interactive demo</h2>
  <div class="demo-placeholder">Interactive demo coming soon</div>
</WidgetLayout>
